            "source": "Re-enable Title Bar",
            "target": "重新启用标题栏"
        },
        {
            "type": "description",
            "source": "Enable this to have a title bar, for example to move the Obsidian window",
            "target": "启用此项以显示标题栏，例如用于移动 Obsidian 窗口"
        },
